Package: lulc
Title: LULC Classification Research Compendium
Version: 0.0.1
Authors@R: c(person('Felipe', 'Carlos', role = c('aut', 'cre'), email = 'felipe.carlos@inpe.br'),
             person('Felipe', 'Souza', role = c('aut'), email = 'felipe.carvalho@inpe.br')
             )
Maintainer: Felipe Carlos <felipe.carlos@inpe.br>
Description: This package is the materialization of a Research Compendium (RC), 
        created based on the annotations made by Marwick et al. (2017). <10.1080/00031305.2017.1375986>. 
        This RC implements the complete flow described in Simoes et al. (2021) <doi:10.3390/rs13132428> 
        for generating land use and land cover maps using Earth Observation Data Cubes and Machine Learning 
        algorithms.
Encoding: UTF-8
Language: en-US
